data.title: Paul Thomas Anderson's 'Licorice Pizza' is an endearing slice of '70s Hollywood
data.meta_description: An enterprising teen and a 20-something photographer's assistant become unlikely friends — and then zig-zag from one comic episode to the next — in this altogether wonderful film.
